                        p Trojena is part of NEOM&apos;s regional plan, located 50km from the Gulf of Aqaba coast in the heart of our nature region. Elevations range from 1,500m to 2,600m and cover an area of nearly 60 square kilometers. Ideally located for alpine and adventure sports, Trojena experiences sub-zero winter temperatures and has a year-round moderate climate that is cooler on average than the rest of the region. With its clear fresh air and panoramic views, Trojena will not only be a mesmerizing place to visit, but also the perfect place to live and work.
